,
\begin_inset Formula ${\bf b}\in\mathbb{R}^{n},\det({\bf A})\neq0.$
\end_inset

如果方程组
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
{\bf Ax=b\iff x=Bx+f}
\]

\end_inset

